metadata.name: genPepes
metadata.description:
Feels Good.

Additional Info:  
On every refresh, a Pepe design is randomly chosen and drawn with random shapes.

Interactivity:  
Use keys 1-7 to select a pepe design. Use 'R' to toggle rotation mode, which when activate will randomly cycle through the designs every 2400, 4800, and 9600 cycles. Use keys 8-0 to select a rotation delay. Use 'A' to set the most abstract settings. Use the left and right arrows to change the shape size and framerate. Use 'F' to reset all your nonsense.

Domains:  
"genPepes.com" and the decentralized domain "genPepes.nft" route to the generative content stored on IPFS.  
"genPepes.eth" is pointed at the genPepes smart contract.
